<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Culture_in_the_14th_century"><span class="tocnumber">2.18</span> <span class="toctext">Culture in the 14th century</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Jagiellon_Era"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Jagiellon Era</span></a></li>
